      • getExtensions

        public static <S extends Scheme> java.util.Collection<SchemeImporterEP<S>> getExtensions(java.lang.Class<S> schemeClass)
        Finds extensions supporting the given schemeClass
        Parameters:
        schemeClass - The class of the scheme to search extensions for.
        Returns:
        A collection of importers capable of importing schemes of the given class. An empty collection is returned if there are no matching importers.

      • getImporter

        public static <S extends Scheme> SchemeImporter<S> getImporter(java.lang.String name,
                                                               java.lang.Class<S> schemeClass)
        Find an importer for the given name and scheme class. It is allowed for importers to have the same name but different scheme classes.
        Parameters:
        name - The importer name as defined in plug-in configuration.
        schemeClass - The scheme class the importer has to support.
        Returns:
        The found importer or null if there are no importers for the given name and scheme class.
